In bug 212185, the transformers and artifacts were implemented for the Service Metadata functionality specified in CMDBf 1.0. The remaining work to utilize these classes within the SML repository expose the metadata in the MDR is to be done under this enhancement. See the design document for http://wiki.eclipse.org/COSMOS_Design_212185 for more details of the remaining work.
Bill, please update the design to include design details for this work, and also update this enhancement to indicate the enhancements on which this depends (i.e. the COSMOS contribution manager supporting the IPolicyAssertion interface of the data manager during the WSDL generation).

Created attachment 88006 Patch for ws-policy
Multi-project patch to enable injection of ws-policy information into wsdl returned by cosmos.

Changed have been submitted.
Note to QA: Please use the COSMOS Client application to test this ER. Refer to the "Test coverage" section on the design page for detail instructions.
QA Review for JUnits and Manual Tests: - Found Manual Tests under design doc and has been executed as part of QA End2End testing. No issues found.
